name: ABUS ALUMINIUM COMBINATION PADLOCK
description:
The ABUS 145 Series Aluminium Combination Padlocks feature resettable combinations. The lock body is made from solid aluminium with an anodized coating that is corrosion resistant. Fitted with a spring loaded steel shackle for better setting of the opening code.

As the padlocks are secured by means of a 3-digit or 4-digit number combination that can be set individually, they are ideal for use in the leisure industry as there is no need to carry a key. They are also ideal for securing items of luggage or tool boxes.

20-30mm: 3 digit combination, to secure valuables/goods of lesser value or at a low risk of theft.

40mm: 4 digit combination, to secure valuables/goods of medium value or at an average risk of theft.
categories: TOOLS/PADLOCKS, DOOR LOCKS & SECURITY/PADLOCKS AND HASP & STAPLES/ABUS PADLOCKS

name: BAHCO COMBINATION AUGER BIT
description:
The Bahco 9626 Series Combination Auger Bits are made from hardened tool steel and lacquered for rust protection. Spirals with Levin pattern. Can be used in both electric power drills and hand braces. Part of the tang has a hexagonal shank (15mm long) for a firm grip in the chuck, suitable for hand braces.

The threaded tip moderates a self-feed when using a power drill, but still sufficient self-feed when used in a hand brace. Ideal for quick precision cutting with all types of wood.

description:
THE DEWALT DCD796 XR BRUSHLESS G2 COMBI DRILL FEATURES 2ND GENERATION BRUSHLESS TECHNOLOGY FOR 30% MORE POWER AND EXCELLENT EFFICIENCY. IT HAS AN ULTRA-COMPACT, LIGHTWEIGHT DESIGN THAT MAKES IT PERFECT FOR USE IN CONFINED SPACES. THE 2-SPEED ALL-METAL TRANSMISSION PROVIDES INCREASED RUN TIME AND LONGER TOOL LIFE WITH DRILL DRIVER AND HAMMER FEATURES FOR MULTIPLE APPLICATIONS.  IT OFFERS A 15-POSITION ADJUSTABLE TORQUE CONTROL FOR CONSISTENT SCREWDRIVING INTO A VARIETY OF MATERIALS. INTELLIGENT TRIGGER DESIGN AND AN ERGONOMICALLY DESIGNED HANDLE FOR OPTIMUM COMFORT AND CONTROL. THE  FLEX TORQUE IMPACT BIT SET IS SUPPLIED IN A ROBUST SMALL CASSETTE FOR SAFE STORAGE AND EASY ACCESSIBILITY TO SCREWDRIVING ACCESSORIES. IT IS IMPACT READY, FOR USE IN IMPACT DRIVERS. THE MAGNETIC BIT TIP HOLDER FEATURES A RETRACTABLE COLLAR TO EJECT THE SCREWDRIVER BIT ONLY WHEN THE USER WANTS TO REMOVE IT. CONTAINS:  3 X 25MM SLOTTED SCREWDRIVING BITS: SL6, SL8 AND SL105 X 25MM PHILLIPS SCREWDRIVING BITS: PH1, PH2(X3) AND PH32 X 25MM PHILLIPS DRYWALL BITS: PR2(X2)10 X 25MM POZIDRIV SCREWDRIVING BITS: PZ1(X2), PZ2(X5) AND PZ3(X3)11 X 25MM TORX SCREWDRIVING BITS: TX10(X2), TX15(X2), TX20(X2), TX25(X2), TX27, TX30 AND TX401 X MAGNETIC BIT TIP HOLDER  SPECIFICATION:  CHUCK: 13MM KEYLESSNO LOAD SPEED: 0-550/0-2,000/MIN.IMPACT RATE: 0-9,350/34,000/BPMMAX. TORQUE: 70NM, 15 
SETTINGSCAPACITY: STEEL 13MM, MASONRY 13MM, WOOD 40MM

name: DCF620D2K BRUSHLESS COLLATED DRYWALL SCREWDRIVER 18V 2 X 2.0AH LI-ION
description:
THE DEWALT DCF620D2K BRUSHLESS COLLATED DRYWALL SCREWDRIVER IS IDEAL FOR EFFICIENT FITTING OF DRYWALL. IT HAS A POWERFUL BRUSHLESS MOTOR THAT DRIVES SCREWS EFFICIENTLY AND EFFECTIVELY AND WHICH OFFERS MAXIMUM RUNTIME.  THIS DRYWALL SCREWDRIVER IS ONE OF THE LIGHTEST AND MOST COMPACT TOOLS ON THE MARKET MAKING IT IDEAL FOR USE IN TIGHT SPACES. ITS QUICK RELEASE COLLATED SCREW MAGAZINE ACCEPTS MOST COLLATED SCREWS TO ALLOW THE USER TO FIT BOARDS MORE QUICKLY. THE MAGAZINE ROTATES ON THE TOOL WITHOUT REMOVAL TO ALLOW USE IN CORNERS WITH MINIMUM FUSS.  THE DCF620D2K FEATURES TOOL FREE DEPTH CONTROL AND FINE DEPTH CONTROL FOR SIMPLE BUT EFFECTIVE SETTING. ITS LED WORKLIGHT OFFERS VALUABLE LIGHT WHEN WORKING IN SMALL SPACES OR AREAS WITH LIMITED LIGHT. A TRIGGER LOCK ALLOWS COMFORTABLE, PROLONGED WORK.  THE DCF620D2K HAS AN ERGONOMICALLY DESIGNED RUBBER GRIP FOR EXCELLENT USER COMFORT WHILST USING THE TOOL IN EITHER THE 'IN-LINE' OR 'PISTOL-GRIP' HAND POSITION. IT IS ALSO SUPPLIED WITH LOCKING NOSE CONE, ALLOWING WORK WITH THE SAME TOOL ON SITES WHERE COLLATED DRYWALL SCREWS ARE NOT SUPPLIED. THE 'SET AND FORGET' FEATURE REMEMBERS YOUR FINE DEPTH ADJUSTMENT SETTING WHEN REMOVING AND REPLACING THE NOSE CONE.  SUPPLIED WITH: 2 X 18 VOLT 2.0AH XR LI-ION BATTERIES, 1 X MULTI-VOLTAGE XR CHARGER, 1 X DCF6201 COLLATED SCREW MAGAZINE, 1 X DT7205-QZ PR2 COLLATED SCREW BIT, 1 X SINGLE SCREW NOSE CONE, 1 X DT7520-QZ MAGNETIC BIT EXTENDER WITH 25MM PR2 SCREW BIT AND 1 X TSTAK 2 KITBOX.  
SPECIFICATION  BIT HOLDER: 6.35MM (1/4IN).NO LOAD SPEED: 0-4,400/MIN.TORQUE: 5-30NM.COLLATED HEAD CAPACITY: 55MM.WEIGHT: 1.88KG.

name: DT2440L 2X LIFE RECIPROCATING SAW BLADE 6 PIECE SET
description:
THE DEWALT 2X LIFE RECIPROCATING SAW BLADE 6 PIECE SET CONTAINS A MIXTURE OF BLADE TYPES FOR A WIDE RANGE OF CUTTING JOBS AND IS SUPPLIED IN A HASSLE-FREE, RE-USABLE STORAGE CASE THAT QUICKLY AND EASILY ADJUSTS TO SUIT THE BLADE LENGTHS.  THEY HAVE SUPERIOR HSS (HIGH SPEED STEEL) TEETH WITH ADDED COBALT FOR HARDER, STRONGER TEETH WITH GREATER FLEX FOR EXCELLENT CUTTING PERFORMANCE AND LONG LIFE EVEN IN THE MOST DEMANDING APPLICATIONS. FAST AND ACCURATE CUTTING IN WOOD APPLICATIONS THANKS TO THE PLUNGE POINT TIP TECHNOLOGY WHICH PIERCES THE WOOD AND REMOVES MORE MATERIAL.  THEY HAVE AN OPTIMISED BLADE DESIGN OFFERING INCREASED HEIGHT AND THICKNESS FOR STURDINESS, STRENGTH AND EXTREME DURABILITY. THE TOUGHCOAT HARDENED COATING LOWERS SURFACE FRICTION AND REDUCES HEAT BUILD UP TO PROMOTE LONG BLADE LIFE. THEY HAVE AN AGGRESSIVE SHANK ANGLE THAT INCREASES TOOTH ENGAGEMENT IN ALL MATERIALS AND EXTENDS BLADE LIFE.  THE METAL BLADES HAVE AN OPTIMISED TOOTH DESIGN WITH A 14/18 TPI VARIABLE TOOTH GEOMETRY REDUCES TOOTH BREAKAGE IN HARD METALS FOR EXTREME DURABILITY EVEN IN THE MOST DEMANDING APPLICATIONS.  CONTAINS:  1 X DT2307L 2X LIFE WOOD & NAIL RECIPROCATING BLADE 228MM, 6 TPI.1 X DT2308L 2X LIFE GENERAL PURPOSE RECIPROCATING BLADE, 10 TPI.1 X DT2300L 2X LIFE WOOD & NAIL RECIPROCATING BLADE 152MM, 6 TPI.1 X DT2301L 2X LIFE GENERAL PURPOSE RECIPROCATING BLADE 152MM, 10 TPI.1 X DT2407L 2X LIFE METAL RECIPROCATING BLADE 152MM, 14/18 TPI.1 X DT2315L 2X LIFE GENERAL PURPOSE RECIPROCATING B
LADE 100MM, 10 TPI.
categories: TOOLS/POWER TOOL ACCESSORIES/BLADES/RECIPROCATING SAW BLADE

name: MSS 1610 MITRE SAW STAND
description: THE EINHELL MSS 1610 MITRE SAW STAND BRINGS STABILITY INTO YOUR WORKSHOP. THE SOLID ALUMINIUM CONSTRUCTION PROVIDES A HIGHLY SECURE UNDERFRAME FOR SLIDING MITRE SAWS AND OTHER STATIONARY MACHINES. MOUNTING OF LARGER ITEMS (UP TO 455MM) IS POSSIBLE WHEN THE MOUNTING BRACKETS ARE EXTENDED. THE SIDE EXTENSIONS ARE EQUIPPED WITH WORKPIECE PROTECTING ROLLERS.  THERE IS ONE HEIGHT-ADJUSTABLE FOOT, WHICH GUARANTEES STABILITY, EVEN ON UNEVEN GROUND. DETACHABLE BRACKETS MEAN THAT THE MOUNTED MACHINE IS STILL MOBILE AND CAN BE PLACED AT ANOTHER WORKBENCH FOR EXAMPLE. WITH ERGONOMIC QUICK CLAMPS FOR EASY FEET AND SIDE EXTENSION FIXATION.  OTHER USEFUL FEATURES INCLUDE: 2 X STORAGE BOXES IN THE MAIN TABLE TO STORE SMALL PARTS SUCH AS SCREWS OR NAILS AND 2 X WORKPIECE STORAGE CLAMPS ON THE FRONT FEET.  IDEAL FOR JOBS AT THE BUILDING SITE OR IN THE WORKSHOP.  SPECIFICATION:  MAX. LOAD: 100KG.MOUNTING NUT SIZE: 8MM.WEIGHT: 12.52KG.

name: FLEXIBLE DRIVE SHAFT 1.1M 6MM CAPACITY
description: A 1.1M (43IN) LONG FLEXIBLE DRIVE SHAFT THAT WILL FIT DIRECTLY INTO THE CHUCK OF ANY CORDLESS OR ELECTRIC POWER DRILL.  THE REINFORCED ENDS AND ANTI-KINK DESIGN PREVENTS WEAR AND HELPS PROVIDE A LONG WORKING LIFE.  A 6MM (1/4IN) CAPACITY KEYLESS CHUCK MAKES CHANGING BITS EASY AND THE PLASTIC HAND GRIP PROVIDES A FIRM HOLD MAKING THE SHAFT EASY TO GUIDE WHEN IN USE.  USING A FLEXIBLE DRIVE ENABLES YOU TO TAKE YOUR POWER TOOL TO THE MOST INACCESSIBLE PLACES.  IT MAY BE USED WITH DRILL BITS, WIRE BRUSHES, COUNTERSINKS, FLAP WHEELS, MOUNTED STONES AND GRINDING WHEELS.  PLEASE NOTE: - THE 6MM SHANK IS NOT HEX AS DESCRIBED ON THE PACKAGING IT IS ROUND.

name: SDS PLUS CIRCULAR CUTTER
description: FAITHFULL ELECTRICAL BACK BOX CUTTERS ARE A LABOUR AND TIME SAVING SYSTEM, DESIGNED TO CUT SOCKETS IN BLOCKWORK AND BRICK WALLS FOR THE SITING OF ELECTRICAL BACK BOXES. THEY ARE USED IN CONJUNCTION WITH LIGHTWEIGHT 2KG SDS FIXING HAMMERS WITH A ROTATION STOP FUNCTION.  THIS TCT CUTTER BIT IS DESIGNED FOR USE WITH FAITHFULL BOX CUTTERS TO FORM RECESSES FOR EITHER SINGLE OR DOUBLE ELECTRICAL BACK BOXES. IT CUTS 77MM ROUND HOLES IN BLOCK, SOFT BRICK AND CONCRETE. THE CUTTER HAS PRECISION MACHINED CUTTING EDGES AND IS DESIGNED FOR USE WITH 2KG SDS PLUS ROTARY HAMMER DRILLS.  CUTTER BIT SIZE: 77MM  SET INCLUDES:1 X SDS PLUS SHANK DRILL 8 X 160MM.1 X SDS PLUS FLAT CHISEL 20 X 140MM.  USE IN CONJUNCTION WITH FAISDSBOXSML AND FAISDSBOXLRG BOX CUTTERS TO FORM RECESSES FOR ELECTRICAL BACK BOXES.

name: CHE 18.0-EC BRUSHLESS SDS DRILL 18V BARE UNIT
description: THE FLEX CHE 18.0-EC BRUSHLESS SDS DRILL HAS A BRUSHLESS MOTOR WITH GREATER EFFICIENCY AND A LONGER SERVICE LIFE. THE ROBUST GEARBOX HOUSING IS MADE FROM DIE-CAST ALUMINIUM. THE ACCELERATOR TRIGGER SWITCH HAS A LOCKING FUNCTION THAT HELPS TO PREVENT FATIGUE. FITTED WITH A BRUSHLESS MOTOR FOR INCREASED POWER AND PERFORMANCE THANKS TO THE IMPROVED ELECTRICAL EFFICIENCY AND POWER TRANSFER. IT HAS A LIGHTWEIGHT AND COMPACT BODY WITH A DUST AND WATER-RESISTANT CONSTRUCTION.  5-STAGE VARIABLE SPEED SYSTEM PLUS AUTO MODE: THE SPEED AUTOMATICALLY SHIFTS BETWEEN HIGH (9,500/MIN.) AND LOW (5,500/MIN.) SPEEDS DEPENDING ON THE LOAD, RESULTING IN MORE EFFECTIVE OPERATION. THIS MACHINE IS PACKED FULL OF SAFETY FEATURES: AN ELECTRONIC BRAKE, KICKBACK PROTECTION SYSTEM, ANTI-RESTART PROTECTION AND SOFT START.  THIS MACHINE UTILISES THE NEXT GENERATION OF 36V BATTERY POWER DEVELOPED FROM USER NEEDS AND HIKOKI'S ORIGINAL TECHNOLOGY. BATTERIES ARE COMPATIBLE WITH EXISTING HITACHI 18V TOOLS. name: IRWIN WOOD AUGER DRILL BIT LONG SERIES
description:
The Irwin long auger wood drill bits have been designed for all general wood boring and offer a superior performance. The single spur cutting edge scribes the circumference of the hole for a smoother quality finish. The hexagon shank prevents slipping in a drill chuck or bit extension.

The solid centre provides extra rigidity whilst boring, the self-feeding screw point provides faster boring in both soft and hard woods and the fully hardened body from tip to shank provides extra durability.

M PACK DURABILITY.  IT IS FITTED WITH A POWERFUL MILWAUKEE® DESIGNED AND BUILT BRUSHLESS POWERSTATE™ MOTOR WITH AN ON BOARD FUEL GAUGE AND AN LED WORK LIGHT.  BARE UNIT, NO BATTERY OR CHARGER. name: R18PD3-113G COMBI DRILL 18V 1 X 1.3AH LI-ION
description: THE RYOBI R18PD3-113G COMBI DRILL IS IDEAL FOR DRILLING WOOD, METAL, MASONRY, PLASTIC, PLASTERBOARD, CERAMIC AND TILES. IT HAS 3 FUNCTIONS; DRILL, HAMMER DRILL AND SCREWDRIVER. THE HAMMER MODE ADDS ADDITIONAL IMPACT FORCE FOR DRILLING HARD MATERIALS SUCH AS BRICK, STONE AND CONCRETE, PERFECT FOR INSTALLING TV BRACKETS, CURTAIN RAILS, OUTDOOR LIGHTS AND SHELVING.  THE 2-SPEED GEARBOX DELIVERS 500/1800RPM AND UP TO 50NM OF TORQUE, PROVIDING VERSATILITY BETWEEN DIFFERENT MATERIALS AND APPLICATIONS. THE 24-TORQUE SETTINGS ALLOW YOU TO DRIVE SCREWS FLUSH EACH TIME FOR A BETTER FINISH, WHILST THE LED LIGHT MAKES IT IDEAL FOR WORK IN POORLY LIT AREAS.  A RATCHETING CHUCK IMPROVES BIT GRIP STRENGTH, MAKING THIS TOOL COMPATIBLE WITH ALL STANDARD ACCESSORY BITS UP TO 13MM. THE INTEGRATED BIT STORAGE CLIP KEEPS THE INCLUDED DOUBLE-ENDED (FLAT HEAD/POZI) BIT STORED ON THE TOOL AND CLOSE AT HAND.  ALL ONE+ BATTERIES AND CHARGERS ARE COMPATIBLE WITH ALL ONE+ TOOLS AND A 3-YEAR WARRANTY IS INCLUDED ACROSS THE ONE+ RANGE.  SPECIFICATION:  CHUCK: 13MMNO LOAD SPEED: 0-500/0-1,800/MIN.IMPACT RATE: 6,500/23,400/BPMTORQUE: 50NM, 24 SETTINGSCAPACITY: STEEL 13MM, MASONRY 13MM, WOOD 38MM
categories: TOOLS/POWER TOOLS/DRILLS - CORDLESS DRILLS

name: RAG800 ANGLE GRINDER 115MM 800W 240V
description: THE RYOBI RAG800 COMPACT ANGLE GRINDER IS EXTREMELY VERSATILE AND HAS A WIDE RANGE OF USES FROM CUTTING AND GRINDING METAL, SHARPENING BLADES, SHAPING STONE OR PAVING TO REMOVING RUST AND LOOSE PAINT OFF METAL AND POLISHING. THE POWERFUL MOTOR AND HIGH TORQUE GEAR BOX MAKES THIS A COMPACT YET POWERFUL TOOL FOR MOST GRINDING APPLICATIONS, PRODUCING A NO LOAD SPEED OF 12,000RPM.  THE CONVENIENT ADJUSTABLE WHEEL GUARD AND SPINDLE LOCK MAKES ACCESSORY AND WHEEL CHANGING QUICK AND EASY. WHILST THE 2-POSITION HANDLE ENSURES COMFORT AND OPTIMUM CONTROL FOR LEFT OR RIGHT HANDED OPERATIONS. AN ADDITIONAL FEATURE IS THE LOCK ON SWITCH PREVENTING FATIGUE AND ALLOWING FOR EASY COMFORTABLE CONTINUOUS USE.  SUPPLIED WITH: 1 X GRINDING WHEEL, 1 X WRENCH, 1 X AUXILIARY HANDLE AND 1 X WHEEL GUARD.  SPECIFICATION  INPUT POWER: 800W.NO LOAD SPEED: 12,000/MIN.DISC DIAMETER: 115MM.SPINDLE: M14.

name: BICYCLE SET TORQUE 1 CLICK-TORQUE ADJUSTABLE WRENCH SET, 16 PIECE
description: THE WERA BICYCLE SET TORQUE 1 CLICK-TORQUE ADJUSTABLE WRENCH SET CONTAINS THE MOST IMPORTANT TOOLS FOR WORKING ON BICYCLES, WITH RELIABLE CONTROL OF APPLIED TORQUE; TO PROTECT SENSITIVE COMPONENTS.  WERA CLICK-TORQUE WRENCHES FEATURE AN UNMISTAKABLE, EXTREMELY ROBUST DESIGN, WITH AN ERGONOMIC 2-COMPONENT HANDLE, FOR GREAT COMFORT AND GRIP.
